					"value": "Player approaches Lae'zel to enjoy a second night of romance, which will be implied offscreen. This could either trigger at the party if the player already slept with Lae'zel, or any other time between her act 1 and 2 romance scenes. To set the feeling of the sexual relationship becoming a regular thing."
